<br>
And while you may be correct that no other class has their nukes seperated into two specilizations several other classes have to decide what to specilize in.<br>
<br>
Finally, let me add that it seems that some people will never be satisfied.  They just seem to want it all.  This is one of those requests that seems like it belongs on the Druid's Grove.  There are certain things I accept about being a mage: I won't have much defense.  I won't have root.  <br>
<br>
If the only way you will be happy is to remove all the limitations on a class, I submit you will never be happy.<br>
<br>
Traigos<br>
